Class DebugJDD.DebugJDDNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdd.JDDNode
      • jdd.DebugJDD.DebugJDDNode
  • Enclosing class:
    DebugJDD

    protected static class DebugJDD.DebugJDDNode
extends JDDNode
    A DebugJDDNode extends a JDDNode with additional information useful for tracking refs/derefs and tracing.

        private long id
        The ID for this JDDNode. In contrast with the CUDD DdNode* ptr, this will be stable across PRISM invocations and can thus be used for tracing.
